PrecisApproval of the reappointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of OLGA BARRAT, of North Vancouver, British Columbia, and RON FOXCROFT, of Hamilton, Ontario, as trustees of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective September 15, 2001.
